						               													<description>In Defense Grid: The Board Game, a co-operative deck-building game based on the Defense Grid video game franchise, you and your fellow players must face off against waves and waves of aliens as you try to #ProtectTheCores. How you construct your deck for each mission is just as important as where you place your towers and which ones you choose to power each round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Reclamation of Atavio is a Defense Grid: The Board Game campaign expansion consisting of 24 individual scenarios that are narratively and mechanically linked. The scenarios feature a couple of new mechanisms, such as tower unlocks, individual card rewards, Boss-Aliens, and specific map rules, in addition to narration from iconic characters of the computer game such as Fletcher, Cai, Rissler, and others in a novel (non-canon) tale within the lore of Defense Grid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
